      "scepter_upgrade": null,
      "shard_upgrade": "Gains an active component, allowing Visage to use Stone Form, stunning enemies for <span class=\"GameplayVariable\">0.8 / 1.0 / 1.2</span> seconds in an <span class=\"GameplayVariable\">375</span> area around it, dealing <span class=\"GameplayVariable\">60 / 100 / 140</span> damage and becoming invulnerable for <span class=\"GameplayVariable\">6</span> seconds.  Restores up to %shard_hp_restoration_pct%%% of your health.",
